<!DOCTYPE html>
% title "Premium links sent";
% layout 'premium', with_video => 0;
<div class="premium-access-main">
    <img src="<%= url_for '/images/Animals/Owl.jpg' %>" id="premium-access-image" />
    <h1>Premium links sent</h1>
    <p>
    We have sent you an email to the address you entered, listing all the
    premium pages you currently have access to. Don't forget to check
    your spam folder if you don't receive it shortly.
    </p.
    <p>
    If you still can't get to the page you want
    then you can use the <a href="<%= url_for('crp.page', page => 'contact') %>">contact form</a>
    to ask for further help.</p>
    <img src="<%= url_for '/images/Plants/Thistle.png' %>" style="display: block; margin: 20px auto;" />
</div>
